<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77a15807-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s450bb–5"><num value="450bb–5">§ 450bb–5.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums, not to exceed $300,000, as may be necessary for the purchase of lands, interests therein, and improvements thereon pursuant to sections 450bb–3 to 450bb–5 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77a15808-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/655/s3">Pub. L. 86–655, § 3</ref>, <date date="1960-07-14">July 14, 1960</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/74/521">74 Stat. 521</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
